<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَنِيَّةُ الاسْتِبَاحَةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَحَرُمَ وَطْؤُهَا، إِلَّا مَعَ خَوْفِ زِنًى.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَأَكْثَرُ مُدَّةِ النِّفَاسِ:</span> أَرْبَعُونَ يَوْماً.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَالنَّقَاءُ زَمَنَهُ:</span> طُهْرٌ، يُكْرَهُ الوَطْءُ فِيهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَهُوَ كَحَيْضٍ فِي أَحْكَامِهِ،<span class="c5"> غَيْرَ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> عِدَّةٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَبُلُوغٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>